newitem "Blight"
        spr "fmmisprites/blight.tga"
        rarity 0
        type 1
        itemwep "Blight"
        descr "This abhorrent blade weeps with putrescence, spreading its foul essence with every cut. Be careful not to cut yourself with it... unless you've always wanted to be a ghoul, naturally."

newitem "Blinding Glove"
        spr "fmmisprites/blindingglove.tga"
        rarity 0
        type 5
        combatspell 2 "Blindness"
        descr "Already too bright to look at directly, the glove appears to have a way to target enemies and focus its brightness on them. Staring directly into the sun is preferable to coming near this thing."

newitem "Bloodlash Bindings"
        spr "fmmisprites/bloodlashbindings.tga"
        rarity 0
        type 5
        hp 3
        combatspell -1 "Lashes of Blood"
        descr "These bindings drip with fresh blood, tightening rhythmically with the wearer's heartbeat. The blood drawn grants vital strength and lashes out."

newitem "Bloodmoon Pendant"
        spr "fmmisprites/bloodmoonpendant.tga"
        rarity 0
        type 7
        berserker
        hp 3
        varregen 2
descr "A dark ruby set in blackened silver, said to have been blessed under a blood-red moon. The wearer becomes consumed by bloodlust but heals with every heartbeat."

newitem "Bloody Gauntlet"
        spr "fmmisprites/bloodygauntlet.tga"
        rarity 0
        type 5
        berserker
        str 2
        descr "Kill, destroy, annihilate, until nothing is left."

newitem "Bloody Mask"
        spr "fmmisprites/bloodymask.tga"
        rarity 0
        type 3
        combatspell 1 "Bleed"
        hp -3
        descr "Use your blood to make others bleed. If only it didn't hurt so much."

newitem "Boots of the Caravan Master"
        spr "fmmisprites/caravanboots.tga"
        rarity 0
        type 6 
        combatsum -1 "3*Caravan Guard"
        trade 1
        descr "It doesn't matter if the kingdom is on fire, a smart merchant knows that there is always money to be made."

newitem "Boots of the Coward"
        spr "fmmisprites/cowardboots.tga"
        rarity 0
        type 6
        rank -1
        evasion 1
        morale -2
        descr "Run away faster than anyone else! These boots make you incredibly swift and evasive in combat, but everyone will know you're a coward. Including you."

newitem "Boots of the Shaking Earth"
        spr "fmmisprites/bootsofshakingearth.tga"
        rarity 0
        type 6
        combatspell 2 "Tremor"
        descr "Massive impacts can be heard from miles away, as each step taken shakes the earth."

newitem "Bottled Lightning"
        spr "fmmisprites/bottledlightning.tga"
        rarity 0
        type 7
        shockres 50
        combatspell -1 "Lightning Storm"
        descr "Don't shake it. Don't drop it. Definitely don't open it near anything you like. The storm inside wants out, and when released, it jumps from target to target with gleeful destruction."

newitem "Box of Black Powder"
        spr "fmmisprites/blackpowder.tga"
        rarity 0
        type 7
        fireres -50
        fireexpl 10
        nodrop        
        descr "This odd black powder seems rather useless. Out of curiosity, you’ve taken a small amount of it and tried to set it on fire, as you do when you find unknown alchemical reagents. It started burning immediately, produced a lot of smoke, and smelled kinda weird. Now you carry a whole box of this powder around with you, and you’re not really sure why. Maybe you’ll find a use for it someday. Perhaps you could use it to send smoke signals?"

newitem "Bramble Armor"
        spr "fmmisprites/bramblearmor.tga"
        rarity 0
        type 4
        armor 1
        hp 5
        pathboost 7
        poisonspikes 1
        descr "Made of thorny and poisonous brambles, it doesn’t offer much protection. What it does do, is make the wearer a very undesirable target."

