        spr "fmmisprites/branchofcursedoak.tga"
        rarity 0
        type 1
        itemwep "Branch of the Cursed Oak"
        descr "This branch-weapon has killed more people during its manufacture than most swords do in a century, mostly because the craftsmen kept turning into trees while trying to carve a handle. Make sure you hold it by the non-cursed end, unless you've always wanted to retire as a decorative oak."

