newitem "Burnt Shirt"
        spr "fmmisprites/burntshirt.tga"
        rarity 0
        type 4
        hp -2
        mr 1
        combatsum -1 "2*Shade Beast & 1*Shade"
        descr "A charred shirt that appears to have been pulled from the ashes of a forgotten ritual. It smokes endlessly without flame. Its eerie nature summons shades, bound to the wearer's will. Bizarre and unsettling, it seems to offer some resistance against magic, but no physical protection. Wearing it seems to affect your health."

newmonster "Called Dog"
