        spr "fmmisprites/calmingblindfold.tga"
        rarity 0
        type 3
        saner 5
        badsight
        clumsy
        descr "Sometimes, the only way to regain your sanity is by blocking out the world and forgetting all about it."

newitem "Carrion Gauntlets"
        spr "fmmisprites/carriongauntlets.tga"
        rarity 0
        type 5
        hp -1
        diseaseshield 1
        reanimate 3
        combatspell 1 "Reanimation"   # Summon 1 Soulless
        descr "These rancid, rotted gloves leave a sickly smear upon steel and flesh alike. The touch festers wounds and the dead rise where they fall, eager to follow the carrion. Wearing them can't possibly be healthy."

newitem "Cat's Eye"
        spr "fmmisprites/catseye.tga"
        rarity 0
        type 7
        combatsum -1 "Magic Cat Familiar"
        descr "The cost shall be paid in scritches."

