        spr "fmmisprites/celestialtome.tga"
        rarity 0
        type 7
        pathboost 52
        pathboost 61
        pathboost 22
        pathboost 19
        descr "A masterwork on the heavens that contains all the secrets any practitioner could ever hope for, and several that no mortal mind was ever meant to contain."

newitem "Cerebral Helm"
        spr "fmmisprites/cerebralhelm.tga"
        rarity 0
        type 3
        hp 2
        mindexpl 1
        armytrainer 5
        descr "You’ve repeatedly assured the troops that the visibly pulsing brain isn’t yours, and they’ve stopped asking questions because the results are so good. The helm reveals tactical secrets to you that turn your recruits into veterans, though training sessions have become significantly more unsettling."

newitem "Charged Gauntlet"
        spr "fmmisprites/chargedgauntlet.tga"
        rarity 0
        type 5
        protection 1
        shockres 75
        shockaura 2
        descr "A gauntlet crackling with electricity. The spark jumps over to the weapons one wields, and makes every exchange painful for the enemy."

newitem "Chest of the Bullfrog"
        spr "fmmisprites/chestofbullfrog.tga"
        rarity 0
        type 4
        armor 2
        hp 5
        poisonaura 1
        bluntres
        wall
        descr "A moist, rubbery breastplate that smells exactly like you’d expect. It’s excellent for absorbing heavy impacts and scaling walls, but the constant secretion of toxic slime makes it very difficult to make new friends."

newitem "Claws of the Mole King"
        spr "fmmisprites/moleclaws.tga"
        rarity 0
        type 5
        tunnel
        str 1
        descr "Grafted to your hands they make you look hideous, but also allow you to dig freely. Some of the Mole King's strength enters you. A small mercy."

