newitem         "Cupid's Arrow"
spr                 "fmmisprites/cupidsarrow.tga"
rarity                 0
rank                1
type                 1
itemwep                "Cupid's Arrow"
descr                 "It’s pretty rare to find one of these lying around, so it’d be a shame if it was wasted by shooting it from a bow. Luckily there’s another solution… use the arrow like you’d use a dagger and stab your enemies with it! Just pray to Cupid that your target is susceptible, because if your target is immune to Cupid’s charms, a single arrow isn’t going to help you survive for long. On second thought, don't pray to Cupid. He might want to have his arrow back."

