        descr "Fashioned of silver glass that shimmers with moonlight, this circlet acts as a prism for lunar energy. It fractures the light into several lethal beams that descend like silver spears, striking multiple targets with cold, celestial power."

newitem "Moontouched Circlet"
        spr "fmmisprites/moontouchedcirclet.tga"
        rarity 0
        type 3
        combatspell -1 "Touch of the Moon"
        sleepres
        mr 1
        descr "This circlet channels the moon's heavy, quiet influence to force a deep sleep upon the battlefield while protecting the bearer from its own magic. Ensures you remain vigilant while your foes are lost to unnatural dreams."

newitem "Odd Appendage"
        spr "fmmisprites/oddappendage.tga"
