        rarity 0
        type 3
        hp 3
        fireres 25
        coldres 25
        shockres 25
        acidres 25
        poisonres 25
        descr "These strange lights orbit your head. Not only a pleasing lightshow, they also come with some other useful qualities, absorbing some of the energy of incoming elemental attacks. Since they are rather small they can not absorb everything, but they try the best they can."

newitem "Overwatcher Crown"
        spr "fmmisprites/overwatchercrown.tga"
        rarity 0
        type 3
        hp 3
        morale 1
        farsight 1
        descr "This crown bombards the mind with strange visions, whole armies appearing to march from over the hills long before they arrive."

newitem "Painlash Bindings"
        spr "fmmisprites/painlashbindings.tga"
        rarity 0
        type 5
        berserker
        combatspell -1 "Lashes of Pain"
        descr "These bindings are lined with cruel thorns on the inside that bite deep into flesh. Each movement drives them deeper, until the moment they lash outward with maddened fury. The bearer’s torment is transmuted into violence, as wearing these bindings would put anyone into a state of berserking madness."

newitem "Pandora's Box"
