        type 6
        morale 2
        combatsum -1 "5*Pilgrim"
        swamp
        desert
        mountain
        snow
        descr "A pilgrim rarely walks alone. These boots have crossed every corner of Elysium and lived to tell about it. Step forward in these, and others join your pilgrimage. Together, you'll prove that no terrain can stop those who keep walking."

