        morale 1
        combatsum -1 "5*Pilgrim"
        swamp
        desert
        mountain
        snow
        descr "A pilgrim rarely walks alone. Patched a hundred times, faded by a hundred suns. This cloak mark you as a traveler of the long road. Wear it, and strangers nod in recognition, then fall into step beside you. Together, no road is too long."

