newitem "Tablets of Stone"
        spr "fmmisprites/tabletsofstone.tga"
        rarity 0
        shield
        type 1
        itemwep "Tablets of Stone"
        descr "They came as a pair and have some interesting ideas written on them. One tablet says something about how ‘thou shalt not kill’, which seems like bad advice. Never trust a tablet that tells you not to do the thing you’re best at. On second thought, just don’t trust a tablet, I mean what does the tablet know about your life? Since there’s two, you can wield one in each hand and also use them as makeshift shields. They do pack quite a punch."

newitem "Tangleboots"
        spr "fmmisprites/tangleboots.tga"
        rarity 0
        type 6
        tangleres
        combatspell 2 "Tangle Vine"
        descr "Made of living vines, it is impossible to say how or why they might lash out. How they can tell friend from foe is unknown."

newitem "Tarot Cards"
        spr "fmmisprites/tarotcards.tga"
        rarity 0
        type 7
        combatspell 1 "Twist Fate"
        descr "Most people read their fortunes in a quiet tent, as performing a reading mid-battle is generally considered a grave tactical error. Still, you’ve decided that the best time to rewrite fate is when it’s actively trying to kill you."

newitem "Terracotta Armor"
        spr "fmmisprites/terracottaarmor.tga"
        rarity 0
        type 4
        armor 2
        hp 5
        pierceres
        undead
        slashres
        combatsum -1 "5*Terracotta soldier"
        descr "How odd, that this armor would make you look so much like them. Does blood still flow in your veins? What is your skin made of? Can you still think and feel, or has your very brain become like fired clay? Why are they always with you?"

newitem "The March"
        spr "fmmisprites/themarch.tga"
        rarity 0
        type 6
        tangleres
        unaging
        hp 3
        morale 10
        descr "Once the march begins, it can not be stopped. March ever onward, from now until the end of time."

newitem "Thunder Warding Boots"
        spr "fmmisprites/thunderwardingboots.tga"
        rarity 0
