        descr "Alive with static, these boots are imbued with warding power. Wherever the wearer steps, lightning bends harmlessly away."

newitem "Timekeeper's Hourglass"
        spr "fmmisprites/timekeepershourglass.tga"
        rarity 0
        type 7
        unaging
        twistfate
        descr "The sand flows upward as often as down. Time has no meaning for the one who carries this. They act before thought, dodge before strike, age not at all."

newitem "Tiny Hat"
        spr "fmmisprites/tinyhat.tga"
        rarity 0
        type 3
        tiny
        descr "A hat so ridiculously small, it snugly fits into a human palm. Whoever wears it will shrink down to the size of the hat. This seems like a great disadvantage at first, until it becomes clear that the wearer can move just as fast and hit just as hard, except now they are much harder to hit."

